      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesn't even hurt though. if it were something serious like a rupture wouldn't it be super painful? it just feels heavy and quiet. i'm just really tired of the emergency rooms being so slow and expensive. surely it can't be that urgent if there's no pain? i'll just take some ibuprofen and sleep on it, that should be fine right?",
